{"tha-ap213:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap213:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap213:0.3":"Hatthidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap213:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap213:1.2":"dvipadindassa tadino; ","tha-ap213:1.3":"Nagasettho maya dinno, ","tha-ap213:1.4":"isadanto urulhava. ","tha-ap213:2.1":"Uttamattham anubhomi, ","tha-ap213:2.2":"santipadamanuttaram; ","tha-ap213:2.3":"Nagadanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap213:2.4":"sabbalokahitesino. ","tha-ap213:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap213:3.2":"yam naga madadim tada; ","tha-ap213:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap213:3.4":"nagadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap213:4.1":"Atthasattatikappamhi, ","tha-ap213:4.2":"solasasimsu khattiya; ","tha-ap213:4.3":"Samantapasadika nama, ","tha-ap213:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap213:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap213:5.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap213:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap213:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap213:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma hatthidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap213:7.1":"Hatthidayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}